Flask Calculator Web App
A simple web-based calculator built using Python Flask. This app evaluates basic arithmetic expressions entered through an HTML form and displays the result on the same page.

Features
Handles basic arithmetic expressions (e.g., 2+2, 5*6, (8-3)/5)

Displays result dynamically on the same HTML page

Includes error handling for invalid inputs

Tech Stack
Python 3

Flask

HTML (Jinja templating)

